prompts.frontCover: A dynamic and humorous comic book cover illustration for a greeting card. The scene is set on a vibrant, sunny beach with pop-art style waves crashing in the background. In the foreground, transform the people from the reference photo into bold, classic comic book characters. Jordan, from the right in the photo, is comically struggling to carry a giant, oversized birthday cake that is tilting precariously. He has a strained, determined, and funny expression, wearing a plain brown hoodie and dark pants. Lao Lao, from the left in the photo, is laughing joyfully, pointing at the spectacle with one hand and holding a tiny party blower in the other. She is wearing a plain light blue sweatshirt and black pants. A large, explosive comic book sound effect bubble, like "WHUMP?!" or "KABOOM!", is near the teetering cake. The overall color palette is bright and saturated with bold black outlines and Ben-Day dots for shading, characteristic of vintage comics. In the center of the card, integrated into the sky, the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, flowing handwritten cursive script.
